OL,3,CCost-of-living 'top priority' for
OL,4,CGreens as party unveils manifesto
OL,6,FThe Wales Green Party has pledged to
OL,7,Fmake the cost-of-living crisis a "top
OL,8,Fpriority" in its manifesto, as it aims
OL,9,Fto win its first-ever seats in the
OL,10,FSenedd ahead of the 7 May election.
OL,12,FWales Green Party Leader Anthony
OL,13,FSlaughter said people in Wales have
OL,14,Fbeen "shafted" by Welsh Labour
OL,15,FGovernments, leaving many people
OL,16,F"struggling to survive". He promised
OL,17,Fthat their plan will "improve peoples'
OL,18,Flives and bring back hope".
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G1/14
