OL,3,CCost-of-living 'top priority' for
OL,4,CGreens as party unveils manifesto
OL,6,FThe cost-of-living crisis in Wales has
OL,7,Fbeen driven by soaring housing, food
OL,8,Fand energy prices, which has created a
OL,9,Fsignificant drop in disposable income
OL,10,Fsince late 2021.
OL,12,FThe Welsh Greens manifesto launch in
OL,13,FPort Talbot on Tuesday (7 April)
OL,14,Ffocused primarily on tackling this
OL,15,Fissue.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G2/14
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
