OL,3,CCost-of-living 'top priority' for
OL,4,CGreens as party unveils manifesto
OL,6,FNew measures announced include
OL,7,Fintroducing universal childcare for
OL,8,Fchildren aged nine months to four
OL,9,Fyears, extending the current Welsh
OL,10,FGovernment policy which funds
OL,11,Fchildcare primarily for three and four-
OL,12,Fyear-olds.
OL,14,FThey also want to extend free school
OL,15,Fmeals to secondary schools, as well as
OL,16,Fjust primary.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G3/14
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
