PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F462A1775578269
OL,3,CCost-of-living 'top priority' for
OL,4,CGreens as party unveils manifesto
OL,6,FThey pledge to invest in home-grown
OL,7,Fenergy to keep bills down, to tackle
OL,8,Fhomelessness by banning no-fault
OL,9,Fevictions and ensuring refuge
OL,10,Faccommodation for survivors of
OL,11,Fdomestic abuse.
OL,13,FThese go alongside previously
OL,14,Fannounced pledges that aim to bring
OL,15,Fcosts down, including a rent freeze
OL,16,Ffollowed by rent controls to tackle
OL,17,Fhousing expenses and the #1 bus fares.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G4/14
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
