OL,3,CCost-of-living 'top priority' for
OL,4,CGreens as party unveils manifesto
OL,6,FParty Leader Anthony Slaughter said:
OL,7,F"The people of Wales have been shafted
OL,8,Fby a succession of Westminster
OL,9,Fgovernments and Labour rule in Wales -
OL,10,Fleaving so many of us struggling
OL,11,Feveryday just to survive. That's why
OL,12,Fwe have prioritised actions to help
OL,13,Fpeople with the cost-of-living crisis.
OL,15,F"Our vision is a Wales where everyone
OL,16,Fcan live in dignity, is respected, and
OL,17,Fhas a decent standard of living and
OL,18,Fwell-being."
OL,26,@oD@AOU
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G5/14
