OL,3,CCost-of-living 'top priority' for
OL,4,CGreens as party unveils manifesto
OL,6,FThe Greens said it has an important
OL,7,Frole in deciding who gets to be First
OL,8,FMinister, describing themselves as the
OL,9,F'Kingmakers' of this election.
OL,11,FRecent polling for ITV Cymru Wales
OL,12,Fsuggests the Greens could win around
OL,13,F10 seats in May's election, with no
OL,14,Fother party winning an overall
OL,15,Fmajority.
OL,17,FOther key policy announcements
OL,18,Fpublished in the manifesto include:
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G6/14
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
