CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F462A1775578269
OL,3,CCost-of-living 'top priority' for
OL,4,CGreens as party unveils manifesto
OL,6,FIn response to the launch, Welsh
OL,7,FLabour claimed the Greens were playing
OL,8,F"fantasy politics".
OL,10,FThey said: "The Greens are making
OL,11,Fpromises they can't keep and can't
OL,12,Fcost. They say they want more housing,
OL,13,Fbut when they led a council, they
OL,14,Fproposed selling off council housing.
OL,15,FThey say they want to fight climate
OL,16,Fchange but have opposed wind and solar
OL,17,Ffarms.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G7/14
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
