PN,46208
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F462A1775578269
OL,3,CCost-of-living 'top priority' for
OL,4,CGreens as party unveils manifesto
OL,6,F"The Green Party will spend the next
OL,7,Ffour years feeding Plaid Cymru's
OL,8,Fobsession with independence, at the
OL,9,Fexpense of jobs, public services, and
OL,10,Fthe people of Wales.
OL,12,F"They're just another party playing
OL,13,Ffantasy politics with a plan for a
OL,14,Fplan."
OL,16,FLeader of Reform Wales, Dan Thomas
OL,17,Fsaid: "The Green Party, like Plaid,
OL,18,Fare committed to pulling Wales out of
OL,19,Fthe United Kingdom.
OL,26,@nD@AOUtD@AOUyD@GOU
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G8/14
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
