FL,463,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46209
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F462A1775578269
OL,3,CCost-of-living 'top priority' for
OL,4,CGreens as party unveils manifesto
OL,6,F"A Green and Plaid coalition would
OL,7,Fhave consequences for Welsh families
OL,8,Fthat would be counted in pounds and
OL,9,Fpence. Reform believes in making Wales
OL,10,Fricher, not poorer."
OL,12,FA Plaid Cymru spokesperson said: "This
OL,13,Felection offers Wales a historic
OL,14,Fopportunity for change but that change
OL,15,Fis yet to be decided by the people of
OL,16,FWales - with poll after poll showing
OL,17,Ftwo very different futures: Reform's
OL,18,Fdivision versus Plaid Cymru's hope.
OL,26,@rD@TO]
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G9/14
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
