PN,46210
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F462A1775578269
OL,3,CCost-of-living 'top priority' for
OL,4,CGreens as party unveils manifesto
OL,6,F"A Plaid Cymru government will get to
OL,7,Fgrips with Labour's NHS waiting list
OL,8,Fcrisis by creating surgical hubs
OL,9,Facross Wales to get people treated
OL,10,Fquicker. We will support families with
OL,11,Fthe cost of living crisis with #30,000
OL,12,Fworth of free childcare for all
OL,13,Fchildren aged 9 months to 4 years and
OL,14,Fback Welsh-owned businesses while
OL,15,Fcreate good, well-paying jobs across
OL,16,Four country.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                  G10/14
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,463,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46211
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F462A1775578269
OL,3,CCost-of-living 'top priority' for
OL,4,CGreens as party unveils manifesto
OL,6,F"We'll raise literacy and numeracy
OL,7,Fstandards in our schools, and tackle
OL,8,Fchild poverty. And we'll never stop
OL,9,Fdemanding the fairness Wales is owed
OL,10,Ffrom Westminster.
OL,12,F"We are the only party not taking
OL,13,Forders from headquarters in England -
OL,14,Fwith plans made here in Wales, for our
OL,15,Fcommunities, and the only party that
OL,16,Fcan stop Reform in their tracks.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                  G11/14
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
