PN,46212
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F462A1775578269
OL,3,CCost-of-living 'top priority' for
OL,4,CGreens as party unveils manifesto
OL,6,F"Rooted in social justice,
OL,7,Fenvironmental responsibility - with a
OL,8,Ftarget to reach Net Zero by 2040 - and
OL,9,Fbuilding a fairer Wales, only Plaid
OL,10,FCymru has the experience and
OL,11,Fcredibility to turn our ambitions for
OL,12,FWales into reality."
OL,14,FA Welsh Liberal Democrat spokesperson
OL,15,Fsaid: "The Welsh Greens are repeating
OL,16,Fthe same mistake we've seen in
OL,17,FScotland, where the SNP and Greens
OL,18,Fhave spent years of time, and hundreds
OL,19,Fof thousands of pounds of taxpayers'
OL,20,Fmoney focused on independence instead
OL,21,Fof fixing public services.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                  G12/14
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,463,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46213
SC,0013
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F462A1775578269
OL,3,CCost-of-living 'top priority' for
OL,4,CGreens as party unveils manifesto
OL,6,F"Their and Plaid Cymru's plans for
OL,7,FWelsh independence would cost the
OL,8,Fpublic millions and distract from the
OL,9,Freal priorities, like the NHS and
OL,10,Feducation, whilst their policy to
OL,11,Fleave NATO would put our security at
OL,12,Frisk.
OL,14,F"Wales needs practical solutions, not
OL,15,Fcostly distractions."
OL,17,FThe Conservatives have been approached
OL,18,Ffor comment.
OL,26,@wD@UO]
